      buttons you can load and save a Color Scheme profile.
      This allows that &krusader; can have the &tcmd;, &mc;, foo-commander or your custom colors.
      The Color Schemes are stored in <filename>$KDEDIR/share/apps/krusader</filename>,
      the <filename>foo.color</filename> is a binary file that holds the Color Scheme.</para>

      <tip><para>
      A &mc; and &tcmd; Color scheme file is provided.
      Please <link linkend="help_krusader">upload your favorite Color schemes</link> 
      so that they become available for the &krusader; community. Thanks!
      </para></tip>

  </listitem></varlistentry>

</variablelist>


